📦 Cara Pemasangan haqtivist

Berikut panduan lengkap instalasi haqtivist di berbagai platform:

🐧 Linux (Ubuntu/Debian/Termux)

1. Install Go (Jika belum ada)

Untuk Ubuntu/Debian:

```bash
# Update package
sudo apt update

# Install Go
sudo apt install golang-go -y

# Atau install versi terbaru
wget https://go.dev/dl/go1.21.5.linux-amd64.tar.gz
sudo tar -C /usr/local -xzf go1.21.5.linux-amd64.tar.gz
echo 'export PATH=$PATH:/usr/local/go/bin' >> ~/.bashrc
source ~/.bashrc
```

Untuk Termux (Android):

```bash
# Update package
pkg update && pkg upgrade

# Install Go
pkg install golang

# Install git
pkg install git
```

2. Download dan Install haqtivist

```bash
# Buat folder khusus
mkdir ~/haqtivist
cd ~/haqtivist

# Buat file haqtivist.go (copy script dari atas)
nano haqtivist.go
# Paste seluruh script, simpan dengan Ctrl+X, Y, Enter

# Atau download langsung (jika sudah diupload ke GitHub)
# git clone https://github.com/username/haqtivist.git
# cd haqtivist
```

3. Compile haqtivist

```bash
# Compile untuk Linux
go build -o haqtivist haqtivist.go

# Jika ingin ukuran lebih kecil (strip debug info)
go build -ldflags="-s -w" -o haqtivist haqtivist.go

# Compile untuk ARM (Termux/Raspberry Pi)
GOOS=linux GOARCH=arm go build -o haqtivist haqtivist.go
```

4. Install ke System (Opsional)

```bash
# Pindahkan ke /usr/local/bin
sudo mv haqtivist /usr/local/bin/

# Atau buat alias
echo 'alias haqtivist="~/haqtivist/haqtivist"' >> ~/.bashrc
source ~/.bashrc
```

🪟 Windows

1. Install Go

· Download Go dari: https://go.dev/dl/
· Pilih go1.21.5.windows-amd64.msi
· Install seperti biasa

2. Install haqtivist

Menggunakan Command Prompt (Admin):

```cmd
# Buat folder
mkdir C:\haqtivist
cd C:\haqtivist

# Buat file haqtivist.go (gunakan notepad)
notepad haqtivist.go
# Paste script, save as UTF-8

# Compile
go build -o haqtivist.exe haqtivist.go
```

Menggunakan PowerShell:

```powershell
# Buat folder
New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path C:\haqtivist
Set-Location C:\haqtivist

# Compile
go build -o haqtivist.exe haqtivist.go
```

3. Tambahkan ke PATH (Opsional)

```powershell
# Set environment variable
[Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable("Path", $env:Path + ";C:\haqtivist", [EnvironmentVariableTarget]::User)
```

🍎 MacOS

```bash
# Install Go via Homebrew
brew install go

# Atau download dari website
wget https://go.dev/dl/go1.21.5.darwin-amd64.pkg
# Install package

# Buat folder dan compile
mkdir ~/haqtivist
cd ~/haqtivist
nano haqtivist.go
