🐳 Docker (Alternative - No Go installation needed)

Buat file Dockerfile:

```dockerfile
FROM golang:1.21-alpine

WORKDIR /app

COPY haqtivist.go .

RUN go build -o haqtivist haqtivist.go

ENTRYPOINT ["./haqtivist"]
```

Build dan run:

```bash
# Build image
docker build -t haqtivist .

# Run
docker run --rm haqtivist -target https://example.com -threads 10 -duration 5
```

📱 Termux (Android) - Lengkap

```bash
# 1. Update Termux
pkg update && pkg upgrade

# 2. Install dependencies
pkg install golang git nano

# 3. Buat folder dan script
mkdir ~/haqtivist
cd ~/haqtivist

# 4. Buat file (copy script dari atas)
cat > haqtivist.go << 'EOF'
# Paste seluruh script disini
EOF

# Atau menggunakan nano
nano haqtivist.go

# 5. Compile untuk ARM
go build -o haqtivist haqtivist.go

# 6. Test run
