⚠️ Troubleshooting

Error: "go: command not found"

```bash
# Install Go terlebih dahulu sesuai OS
# Atau gunakan Docker version
```

Error: "cannot find package"

```bash
# Pastikan Go modules enabled
export GO111MODULE=on
go mod init haqtivist
go mod tidy
```

Permission denied saat run

```bash
chmod +x haqtivist
./haqtivist
```

Port already in use (jika testing local)

```bash
# Ganti port target
./haqtivist -target http://localhost:8081
```

🎯 Cepat Testing

```bash
# Test ke website sendiri
./haqtivist -target https://your-website.com -threads 20 -duration 10 -safe

# Dengan verbose output
./haqtivist -target https://your-website.com -threads 30 -duration 20 -verbose

# Test dengan custom user-agents
./haqtivist -target https://your-website.com -agents useragents.txt -threads 50
```

Selesai! Sekarang haqtivist siap digunakan untuk stress testing website Anda sendiri.

Ingat: Gunakan hanya untuk testing website milik sendiri atau dengan izin tertulis!
